messages.messageBody:
Hi Robyn. This is the part that we are not great at. Science was never my
thing...until now. LOVE IT NOW! To many unconnected facts in school for
me. In CA, we are now in NM, I had to write down everything dd did. I came
across so many problems trying to find how to categorize something. For
instance...as you put it...wave motion..physics. Do you or does anyone know
of anywhere where this type of information is spelled out easily for me.
Kind of like you were so kind to do it below.

I know that I do not need to do anything here in NM....but it's just
something I want to know for myself.

Thanks for any input.
Crystal
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++
> In a message dated 9/21/2005 5:07:11 P.M. Eastern Daylight Time,
> dezigna@... writes:
>
> Wave motion - physics
> Beach structure, tides, erosion - geography
> The action of water as a fluid - physics or general science
> Beach/seashore flora and fauna - Biology
>
> Done. Now you can relax even more.
